*The SoC used seems to be QCA9558 (QCA9558-AT4A). :QCA9880 is presumed to be used for the 5 GHz radio, but, as the :FCC photos are not terribly illuminating, the exact P/N is unknown.
Default settings are per ''Linksys'''s manual.
